measurements.description: Fourteen slightly cupped flowers on one 54-cm inflorescence plus five partially open buds on one immature inflorescence; sepals and petals light yellow overlaid oxblood red, darker midline, yellow edges; lip ivory overlaid burgundy distally, picotee, keels white; column pale yellow spotted darker interior surface, anther cap yellow; substance firm; texture matte.
